  "OghmaNotes empowers students and professionals to take better notes, stay organized, and learn more effectively. Our AI-powered platform transforms how you capture and manage knowledge.": "OghmaNotes 使学生和专业人士能够更好地记笔记、保持条理并更有效地学习。 我们的人工智能平台改变了您获取和管理知识的方式。",
