  "Upload a .zip file to import folders and notes. Supports PDF, DOCX, Markdown, and more. Max 10GB.": "Upload a .zip file to import folders and notes. Supports PDF, DOCX, Markdown, and more. Max 10GB.",
  "Upload any PDF or document. The system extracts text, chunks it semantically, and stores embeddings in our vector database. When you ask a question, it retrieves relevant material and generates answers with direct citations so you know where information came from.": "上传任何 PDF 或文档。 该系统提取文本，按语义对其进行分块，并将嵌入存储在我们的矢量数据库中。 当您提出问题时，它会检索相关材料并生成带有直接引用的答案，以便您知道信息来自哪里。",
  "Upload PDFs. Ask questions with cited answers. Generate adaptive quizzes. Master your materials with spaced-repetition flashcards and Canvas sync. Offline-first learning, designed for busy students.": "上传 PDF。 提出问题并引用答案。 生成自适应测验。 使用间隔重复抽认卡和画布同步来掌握您的材料。 离线优先学习，专为忙碌的学生而设计。",
