  "We own our work end-to-end, from code quality to user experience, ensuring reliability you can count on.": "我们对我们的工作进行端到端的掌控，从代码质量到用户体验，确保您可以信赖的可靠性。",
  "We practice what we preach — constantly learning, iterating, and improving our platform based on feedback.": "我们言出必行——根据反馈不断学习、迭代和改进我们的平台。",
  "We sent a verification link to your email. Click the link to verify your account.": "We sent a verification link to your email. Click the link to verify your account.",
  "We strive for excellence in every feature we build, ensuring students get the best possible learning tools.": "我们在构建的每个功能上都力求卓越，确保学生获得最好的学习工具。",
  "We use the SM-2 algorithm to schedule flashcard reviews at optimal intervals. The system learns which cards you struggle with and prioritizes them, scientifically proven to improve long-term retention.": "我们使用 SM-2 算法以最佳间隔安排抽认卡复习。 该系统会了解您对哪些卡片感到困惑，并对其进行优先级排序，科学证明可以提高长期保留率。",
  "We're a dynamic group of individuals who are passionate about what we do and dedicated to creating the best learning platform.": "我们是一个充满活力的团队，对我们所做的事情充满热情，并致力于创建最好的学习平台。",
  "We're changing the way people learn": "我们正在改变人们的学习方式",
  "Week": "Week",
  "Week view": "Week view",
  "What are spaced repetition flashcards?": "什么是间隔重复抽认卡？",
  "What is OghmaNotes?": "OghmaNotes 是什么？",
  "What students say": "学生评价",
  "Whether you're in the classroom, attending lectures, or conducting research, OghmaNotes is designed to help you learn smarter, faster, and with greater retention.": "无论您是在课堂上、参加讲座还是进行研究，OghmaNotes 都旨在帮助您更聪明、更快速地学习并提高记忆力。",
  "Work Anywhere": "随时随地工作",
  "Write beautiful, formatted notes with live preview, syntax highlighting, and seamless organization.": "通过实时预览、语法突出显示和无缝组织编写精美的格式化笔记。",
  "Yes! OghmaNotes is a Progressive Web App. Write and edit notes offline, and they sync automatically when you reconnect. Perfect for lecture halls and studying anywhere.": "是的！ OghmaNotes 是一个渐进式 Web 应用程序。 离线编写和编辑笔记，当您重新连接时它们会自动同步。 非常适合演讲厅和任何地方学习。",
  "Yes. Connect your Canvas account and OghmaNotes automatically syncs your courses, assignments, and deadlines daily. All your course materials are organized in one place with integrated calendar views.": "是的。 连接您的 Canvas 帐户，OghmaNotes 每天自动同步您的课程、作业和截止日期。 您的所有课程材料都组织在一个位置，并具有集成的日历视图。",
